      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver under version control with documented release notes; no bespoke user subroutines requiring independent verification.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 used under institutional licence with version-controlled case files stored in Git. Release notes confirm no open defects affecting rotating-machinery hemolysis simulations. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 2."
    },
    {
