      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters (geometry, flow rates, rotational speeds, fluid properties) demonstrably equivalent to test conditions within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "CAD geometry used in simulation verified against pump drawings with dimensional deviations < 0.05 mm. Flow rates and rotational speeds in simulation match test-rig set-points within 0.3% and 0.5% respectively. Fluid viscosity in simulation set to measured laboratory value. Equivalency established for the laboratory test environment. No equivalency assessment performed for the broader deployment environment (temperature 18–28°C, hypobaric conditions, EMI), which falls outside the characterised input space."
    }
